ttps://kotaku.com/mortal-kombat-1-mk1-review-is-it-good-ps5-xbox-pc-1850863299\">Mortal Kombat 1</a> players are doing everything they can to avoid buying cosmetics in NetherRealms\u2019 latest 2D fighter. The latest exploit involves them utilizing a console date change hack to acquire once-free character skins that are now only available if you buy them.</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/mortal-kombat-1-console-date-change-free-skins-1851040158\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/mortal-kombat-1-console-date-change-free-skins-1851040158", "date_published": "2023-11-21T21:30:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/13613c47346135341e96e051dcea7109.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "I'm So Tired Of Crossover 'Skins' Cluttering Up Video Games", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/22479c0ac62880f86c4fb54e2273706c.jpg\" /><p>Another day, another big video game crossover. This time it\u2019s Bungie\u2019s online looter shooter, Destiny 2, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/destiny-2-final-shape-witcher-3-armor-1851039398\">adding Witcher 3-inspired armor to its digital store</a>. Are you excited? I\u2019m not. In reality, I\u2019m just really tired of <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/iron-giant-multiversus-wb-smash-fighting-game-superman-1848945122\">every brand mixing together</a>, regardless of whether it makes sense or is needed, as if concocting\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/crossover-skins-destiny-2-witcher-halo-rainbow-six-bad-1851039973\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/crossover-skins-destiny-2-witcher-halo-rainbow-six-bad-1851039973", "date_published": "2023-11-21T21:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/22479c0ac62880f86c4fb54e2273706c.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Baldur\u2019s Gate 3 Deluxe Edition Will Defy An Exasperating Trend", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/03d132ce398257e8f0dc355a97b7e59a.jpg\" /><p>Buying super special \u201ccollector\u2019s editions\u201d of video games can be like heading into treacherous waters. These often-expensive boxes full of goodies (and also a video game) tend to sell out pretty quickly, and then you\u2019re more likely to find them for double the price on reseller sites like eBay or Facebook\u2019s\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/baldurs-gate-3-deluxe-edition-reseller-ebay-scarcity-1851039857\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/baldurs-gate-3-deluxe-edition-reseller-ebay-scarcity-1851039857", "date_published": "2023-11-21T20:30:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/03d132ce398257e8f0dc355a97b7e59a.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "The Best Games Of 2023 (So Far) [Updated]", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2c3fbab9e6c52b31648662a351d2b9a7.jpg\" /><p>It\u2019s almost the end of the year of our lord 2023, and every time we\u2019ve updated this compilation of the best games we played, we\u2019ve reflected on just how many good games came out this year. This final update before we start our Game of the Year discussions at Kotaku has some real bangers, big and small. As great as\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/best-video-games-2023-ps5-xbox-series-switch-pc-gaming-1850124419\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/best-video-games-2023-ps5-xbox-series-switch-pc-gaming-1850124419", "date_published": "2023-11-21T20:00:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/2c3fbab9e6c52b31648662a351d2b9a7.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Sony Fails To Kill $7.9 Billion Lawsuit Over PlayStation Store Prices", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e9b0b5acab4733c9e9009fe1dd7eb8d9.jpg\" /><p>A lawsuit filed last year accused Sony of using its walled-garden video game platform to charge players too much in the PlayStation Store. The London Tribunal has now allowed that lawsuit to move forward, against the PS5 maker\u2019s objections, which could result in payments to players in the UK of <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.reuters.com/technology/sony-facing-79-bln-mass-lawsuit-over-playstation-store-prices-2023-11-21/#:~:text=LONDON%2C%20Nov%2021%20(Reuters),London%20tribunal%20ruled%20on%20Tuesday.\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">up to $7.9 billion</a> if\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/playstation-store-lawsuit-ps5-sony-1851039664\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/playstation-store-lawsuit-ps5-sony-1851039664", "date_published": "2023-11-21T19:32:31+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e9b0b5acab4733c9e9009fe1dd7eb8d9.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Embattled Shooter Destiny 2 Gets Witcher 3 Armor", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b64ef694321eafd0ba01fa71cb22d3e7.jpg\" /><p>The white wolf is coming to Destiny 2 by way of some new cosmetics. Bungie teased a crossover with CD Projekt Red\u2019s beloved RPG The Witcher 3 that will add three new armor sets to make players look like protagonist Geralt of Rivia, at least if they\u2019re willing to shell out $20 or more for a single set. The new skins\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/destiny-2-final-shape-witcher-3-armor-1851039398\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/destiny-2-final-shape-witcher-3-armor-1851039398", "date_published": "2023-11-21T18:30:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/b64ef694321eafd0ba01fa71cb22d3e7.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "This Modern Warfare 3 Gameplay Feature Spices Up A Weak Campaign", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/a5609a52bbb2ccc22b0ca5d2d0b568a3.jpg\" /><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/modern-warfare-3-call-of-duty-open-combat-missions-1851032015\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/modern-warfare-3-call-of-duty-open-combat-missions-1851032015", "date_published": "2023-11-21T18:30:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/a5609a52bbb2ccc22b0ca5d2d0b568a3.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Simpsons Hit & Run 2 Would Have Added Planes, But The Publisher Passed", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/0ca9cc60003bf0d4a40f486c081fd079.jpg\" /><p>The original <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/youtuber-discovers-strange-things-hidden-in-the-simpson-1833359213\">Simpsons: Hit & Run</a>, released 20 years ago in 2003, ended up being a massive hit and sold millions of copies. So a sequel, featuring planes, was planned. But then the publisher shocked everyone when it passed on a sweetheart deal to create more Hit & Run games. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/simpsons-hit-and-run-2-sequel-remake-remaster-planes-1851038958\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/simpsons-hit-and-run-2-sequel-remake-remaster-planes-1851038958", "date_published": "2023-11-21T17:17:19+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/0ca9cc60003bf0d4a40f486c081fd079.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments"