WIII\u2019s\u2026</a></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/mw3-cod-call-of-duty-breacher-drone-1851038854\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/mw3-cod-call-of-duty-breacher-drone-1851038854", "date_published": "2023-11-21T16:46:44+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/03148eeb1107cfe50b3817209762c019.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "I Can\u2019t Miss The Last Of Us If It Won\u2019t Leave", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/1722c0f892d47470d98d86ed5570f32a.jpg\" /><p>Remember when it took us seven years to get a new The Last of Us game? Remember when there was even a question about whether or not we\u2019d ever get a sequel to Naughty Dog\u2019s post-apocalyptic action game because <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/the-last-of-us-tlou-ending-joel-ellie-cure-hbo-show-1850214609\">the ending was so intentionally ambiguous and thought-provoking</a>? Now, it seems we can\u2019t go a year without\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/last-of-us-part-2-remastered-ps5-remake-hbo-show-1851038633\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/last-of-us-part-2-remastered-ps5-remake-hbo-show-1851038633", "date_published": "2023-11-21T16:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/1722c0f892d47470d98d86ed5570f32a.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Kotaku\u2019s Ultimate 2023 Gift Guide", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/691ec70056175e72f0dbc2b83392979d.jpg\" /><p>2023 has been <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/2023-best-year-games-goty-switch-ps5-xbox-1850968555\">one heck of a year</a> for games. The typically slow month of January saw the launch of the critically acclaimed Dead Space remake, the shadow-drop sensation <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/hi-fi-rush-bethesda-marketing-trailer-release-xbox-pc-1850046838\">Hi-Fi Rush</a>, and the just-fine Fire Emblem Engage. And every month since has seen a steady stream of high-profile bangers, from Like a Dragon Ishin and T\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/kotaku-s-ultimate-2023-gift-guide-1851018503\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/kotaku-s-ultimate-2023-gift-guide-1851018503", "date_published": "2023-11-21T15:45:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/691ec70056175e72f0dbc2b83392979d.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Cyberpunk 2077's Incredible Turnaround Will Now Be Preserved Forever", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/8b0f90eed287d047611af3226483554a.jpg\" /><p>As Cyberpunk 2077 approaches its third anniversary, the beleaguered blockbuster is getting a send-0ff to immortalize its unlikely turnaround. CD Projekt Red announced an Ultimate Edition for the sci-fi RPG on November 21 that includes this year\u2019s <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/cyberpunk-2077-phantom-liberty-update-review-idris-elba-1850852291\">Phantom Liberty expansion</a> and the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/cyberpunk-2077-update-2-0-patch-notes-skills-cyberware-1850861309\">massive 2.0 overhaul</a> patch. There will\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/cyberpunk-2077-phantom-liberty-2-0-ultimate-edition-1851038320\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/cyberpunk-2077-phantom-liberty-2-0-ultimate-edition-1851038320", "date_published": "2023-11-21T14:40:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user": null, "language": "en", "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/8b0f90eed287d047611af3226483554a.jpg", "age": null, "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating": 0, "tags": [], "comments": [], "vote": 0}, {"source": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "title": "Admit It, You Don\u2019t Understand Skill-Based Matchmaking (And Neither Do I)", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/5801e586d36f1a94cf7661dd27a0be39.jpg\" /><p>Whenever a new blockbuster first-person shooter drops, gamers limber up so they can once again argue over how multiplayer matches get made and the algorithmic systems that determine who plays against whom and when. The recent release of Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III is no exception\u2014not long after its multiplayer\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/mw3-sbmm-definition-meaning-cod-1851037016\">Read more...</a></p>", "link": "https://kotaku.com/mw3-sbmm-definition-meaning-cod-1851037016", "date_published": "2023-11-21T14:15:00+00:00", "permanent": false, "bookmarked": false, "dead": false, "artist": "Kotaku", "album": "Kotaku", "user"